---
import FAQItem from './FAQItem.astro';
---
<section class="faq" id="faq">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="faq-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Frequently asked</span>
      <h2>Christ Note FAQ.</h2>
      <p class="faq-lede">Everything you need to know about carrying the homily home.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <FAQItem question="What is Christ Note?">
        Christ Note is an iPhone companion for the homily. Record live during Mass, paste a parish livestream link, or photograph your notes — an AI summary surfaces scripture references, themes, and key quotes. Past sermons live in a personal library, sorted by week and season.
      </FAQItem>
      <FAQItem question="How does Christ Note protect my privacy?">
        Recordings are encrypted in transit and at rest. Audio is processed for transcription and immediately discarded — only the text remains. We never sell or share your data, and your library is yours alone.
      </FAQItem>
      <FAQItem question="Can I use Christ Note offline?">
        Recording works offline — Christ Note captures audio on-device whether you have signal or not. Transcription and AI summaries need a connection, but they sync automatically the next time you're online.
      </FAQItem>
      <FAQItem question="Is Christ Note free?">
        A free tier covers a few sermons per month. A premium tier unlocks unlimited recordings, deeper AI summaries, and unlimited library storage.
      </FAQItem>
      <FAQItem question="Is there an Android app?">
        Not yet. Christ Note ships on iPhone first, Spring 2026. Android is on the roadmap — join the waitlist and we'll write when it's ready.
      </FAQItem>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.faq {
  padding: var(--section-y) 0;
}
.faq-head {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: var(--s-12);
}
.faq-head .eyebrow {
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: var(--s-4);
}
.faq-head h2 {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: var(--fs-display-3);
  font-weight: 500;
  margin-bottom: var(--s-3);
}
.faq-lede {
  font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", Georgia, serif;
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: var(--fs-body-lg);
  color: var(--ink-600);
  max-width: 52ch;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.faq-list {
  max-width: 760px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
</style>
